programme.title: Jack Reacher: Never Go Back
programme.desc: When an Army Major is framed for treason, Reacher discovers shes the target of a massive government conspiracy and risks everything to take down the corrupt organisation.

programme.title: The Dark Knight
programme.desc: With the help of Lt. Jim Gordon and District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman sets out to destroy organised crime in Gotham for good. The triumvirate proves effective, but soon find themselves prey to a rising criminal mastermind known as The Joker, who thrusts Gotham into anarchy and forces Batman closer to crossing the fine line between hero and vigilante.

programme.title: Interstellar
programme.desc: With our time on Earth coming to an end, a team of explorers undertakes the most important mission in human history: travelling beyond this galaxy to discover whether mankind has a future among the stars.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol
programme.desc: Blamed for the terrorist bombing of the Kremlin, IMF operative Ethan Hunt (Tom Cruise) is disavowed along with the rest of the agency when the President initiates Ghost Protocol. Left without any resources or backup, Ethan must find a way to clear his agencys name and prevent another attack. To complicate matters further, Ethan is forced to embark on this mission with a team of fellow IMF fugitives whose personal motives he does not fully know.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
programme.desc: With the IMF disbanded, and Ethan out in the cold, the team now faces off against a network of highly skilled special agents, the Syndicate. These highly-trained operatives are hell-bent on creating a new world order through an escalating series of terrorist attacks. Ethan gathers his team and joins forces with disavowed British agent Ilsa Faust, who may or may not be a member of this rogue nation, as the group faces their most impossible mission yet.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
programme.desc: On a dangerous assignment to recover stolen plutonium, Ethan Hunt chooses to save his team over completing the mission, allowing nuclear weapons to fall into the hands of a deadly network of highly-skilled operatives intent on destroying civilization. Now, with the world at risk, Ethan and his IMF team are forced to become reluctant partners with a hard-hitting CIA agent as they race against time to stop the nuclear fallout. Theres never been a threat more destructive, stunts so jaw-dropping in the film critics are calling the best "Mission" yet!

programme.title: Men in Black 3
programme.desc: Agents J and K are back in time. J has seen some inexplicable things in his 15 years with the Men in Black, but nothing, not even aliens, perplexes him as much as his wry, reticent partner. But when Ks life and the fate of the planet are put at stake, Agent J will have to travel back in time to put things right. J discovers that there are secrets to the universe that K never told him, secrets that will reveal themselves as he teams up with the young Agent K to save his partner, the agency and the future of humankind.

programme.title: Man of Steel
programme.desc: A young boy learns that he has extraordinary powers and is not of this Earth. As a young man, he journeys to discover where he came from and what he was sent here to do. But the hero in him must emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind.

programme.title: Spider-Man: No Way Home
programme.desc: With Spider-Mans identity now revealed, Peter asks Doctor Strange for help. When a spell goes wrong, dangerous foes from other worlds start to appear, forcing Peter to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.

Theres never been a threat more destructive, stunts so jaw-dropping in the film critics are calling the best "Mission" yet!

programme.title: Jurassic Park
programme.desc: Eccentric scientist John Hammond plans to open a theme park consisting of live dinosaurs, genetically engineered from DNA. Archaeologists Alan Grant and Ellie Sattler are invited to view the park, only to find themselves being hunted when the dinosaurs break free.

programme.title: Spider-Man
programme.desc: After a radioactive spider bite, a nerdy teen develops keen senses and amazing strength.

programme.title: Skyscraper
programme.desc: Former FBI Hostage Rescue Team leader and U.S. war veteran Will Sawyer now assesses security for skyscrapers. On assignment in Hong Kong he finds the tallest, safest building in the world, The Pearl, suddenly ablaze, and hes been framed for it. A wanted man on the run, Will must find those responsible, clear his name and somehow rescue his family who is trapped inside the building above the fire line.

programme.title: Death Race 4: Beyond Anarchy
programme.desc: Danny Trejo returns as the ruthless bookie, Goldberg, in the wildest, bloodiest, Death Race ever. After a failed attack on inmate and legendary driver, Frankenstein, Black Ops specialist Connor Gibson (Zach McGowan) infiltrates a super-maximum federal prison with one goal - enter the immoral and illegal Death Race and take Frankenstein down. Connor enlists the help of Baltimore Bob (Danny Glover) and Lists (Fred Koehler), and unexpectedly falls in love with bartending beauty Jane (Christine Marzano). Connor will have to fight for more than his life in this brutal world of no guards, no rules, no track, and no fear.

programme.title: Tenet
programme.desc: Armed with only one word, Tenet, and fighting for the survival of the entire world, The Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold into something beyond real time. Not time travel. Inversion.

programme.title: The Accountant
programme.desc: Christian Wolff is a math savant with more affinity for numbers than people. Behind the cover of a small-town CPA office, he works as a freelance accountant for some of the worlds most dangerous criminal organisations. With the Treasury Departments Crime Enforcement Division, run by Ray King, starting to close in, Christian takes on a legitimate client: a state-of-the-art robotics company where an accounting clerk has discovered a discrepancy involving millions of dollars. But as Christian uncooks the books and gets closer to the truth, it is the body count that starts to rise.

programme.title: Scream
programme.desc: After a series of mysterious deaths befalls their small town, an offbeat group of friends led by Sidney Prescott become the target of a masked killer. As the body count begins to risine, Sidney her friends find themselves contemplating the "Rules" of horror films as they find themselves living in a real-life one.

programme.title: Hulk
programme.desc: Scientist Bruce Banner has anger management issues. His quiet life as a brilliant research scientist working with ex-girlfriend Betty Ross conceals a painful past. A freak lab accident reveals Bruces heroic impulses but also unleashes his inner demons. And he becomes the most powerful being on the face of the Earth: a superhero and a monster.

programme.title: Charlies Angels
programme.desc: When a devious mastermind embroils them in a plot to destroy individual privacy, the Angels, aided by their loyal sidekick Bosley, set out to bring down the bad guys. But when a terrible secret is revealed, it makes the Angels targets for assassination.

programme.title: Alexander
programme.desc: This film re-creates the towering, true story of Alexander the Great, who, in the 4th Century BC, conquered Greece, Persia, Afghanistan and India - 90% of the "Known World." Against massive armies of chariots and elephants, he never lost a battle! Visionary, explorer, and dreamer - he was also a tender son, torn by his mothers burning love and ambition, and desperate for his fathers approval. His dream shaped the world we live in today.

programme.title: The Huntsman: Winters War
programme.desc: Evil Queen Ravenna betrays her good sister, Freya, with an unforgivable act, freezing Freyas heart of love and unleashing in her an icy power she never knew she possessed. Retreating to a kingdom far to the north, Freya raises an army of Huntsmen as her protectors, with the only rule that no two of them should ever fall in love.

programme.title: The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor
programme.desc: The OConnells must stop a mummy awoken from a 2000-year-old curse who threatens to plunge the world into his merciless, unending service. Doomed by a wronged sorceress, Zi Yuan, to spend eternity in suspended animation, the ruthless Dragon Emperor and his 10,000 warriors have laid forgotten for eons, entombed in clay as a vast, silent Terracotta Army.

programme.title: The Prestige
programme.desc: The mysterious story of two magicians whose intense rivalry leads them on a lifelong battle for supremacy full of obsession, deceit, and jealousy with dangerous and deadly consequences. From the time that they first met as young magicians on the rise, Robert Anglier and Alfred Borden were competitors. However, their friendly competition evolves into a bitter rivalry making them fierce enemies-for-life and consequently jeopardising the lives of everyone around them. Full of twists and turns, this film is set against the backdrop of turn-of-the-century London.

programme.title: Ripper Street

Seeking our heroes with a dogged persistence is Assistant Commissioner Augustus Dove. He must do all he can to capture Reid before he is able to reveal the truth to the world: the serial killer is Doves brother Nathaniel.

programme.title: Despicable Me
programme.desc: In a happy suburban neighbourhood surrounded by white picket fences and flowering rose bushes sits a black house with a dead lawn. Unbeknownst to the neighbours, hidden deep beneath this home is a vast secret hideout belonging to Gru, a dastardly villain who, along with the help of his many little minions, is planning the biggest heist in the history of the world: hes going to steal the moon!

programme.title: Despicable Me 2
programme.desc: Gru, his adorable girls, and the mischievous Minions are back with a cast of unforgettable new characters in the blockbuster sequel to the worldwide phenomenon. Just as Gru has given up being super-bad to be a super-dad, the Anti-Villain League recruits him to track down a new criminal mastermind and save the world. Partnered with secret agent Lucy Wilde, Gru, along with the wildly unpredictable Minions, must figure out how to keep his cover while also keeping up with his duties as a father. Get ready for more Minion madness.

programme.title: Sinbad: Legend of the Seven Seas
programme.desc: Its high-seas adventure when legendary swashbuckler Sinbad, his loyal pooch Spike, and the daring Princess Marina face off against the trickster Goddess of Chaos and her mischievous monsters.

programme.desc: After a terrifying storm destroys their home, a speedy sloth named Laura and her kooky family move to the big city in their rusted old food truck hoping to make their business a success.

programme.title: Antz
programme.desc: A worker ant changes roles with a soldier ant to woo a forbidden princess.

programme.title: Grand-Daddy Day Care
programme.desc: When Frank Collins (Reno Wilson) suffers from writers block, he decides to start a day care for his father-in-law (Danny Trejo) and other seniors as a way to make quick cash, while giving him time to still work on his next book. Eventually getting a small group to care for, Frank soon learns that these are not your typical seniors and they cant easily be corralled. With a code enforcement officer challenging the legality of his business, and his senior charges getting into all kinds of trouble, Franks work days become anything but effortless. Featuring an all-star cast of TVs greatest stars, Grand-Daddy Day Care is a hilarious story for the young, and young at heart.

programme.title: Christmas with the Kranks
programme.desc: Fed up with the commercial aspects of Christmas, particularly all the money spent and alone for the holiday for the first time in decades, as their daughter has just joined the Peace Corps, grumpy Luther Krank and his sweet wife, Nora, decide to skip Christmas this year and forgo the gifts, the tree, the decorations, the cards, the parties and to spend the dollars saved on a 10-day Caribbean cruise.

programme.title: The Flintstones
programme.desc: Travel back to the stone-age in this big-budget treatment of the worlds favourite prehistoric family! Fred Flintstone, a put-upon blue-collar worker struggling to squeak by, with the help of his best buddy Barney and his wife Wilma. After an aptitude test mix up, Fred Flintstone trades his job as Slate and Company Bronto-crane operator for a vice presidency. But theres trouble brewing in Bedrock: An evil executive and his sinister secretary are now plotting to use Fred as the fall guy in an embezzlement scheme!

programme.title: Madagascar: Escape 2 Africa
programme.desc: Alex, Morty and other zoo animals find a way to escape from Madagascar when the penguins reassemble a wrecked airplane. The precariously repaired craft stays airborne just long enough to make it to the African continent. There the New Yorkers encounter members of their own species for the first time. Africa proves to be a wild place, but Alex and company wonder if it is better than their Central Park home.

programme.title: Fred Claus
programme.desc: This is a story youve never heard before, a hilarious and heart warming comedy about Fred Claus, Santas brother - and complete opposite. After growing up in saintly Nicks shadow, Fred becomes a grouch whos lost his belief in Christmas. Then, one magical December, Fred flies north (first class via reindeer) to find brother Nick is in trouble: a scheming efficiency expert is out to shut down Christmas forever! Expect fun by the sleighful as Fred helps save Christmas and rediscovers the gift of family.

programme.title: Balto
programme.desc: Part husky, part wolf, Balto doesnt know where he belongs. Hes an outcast in Alaska, except to his true friends - Boris, the Russian snow goose, polar bear cubs Muk and Luk, and the beautiful husky, Jenna. Even though hes different, all of Baltos friends recognise what he still cant see himself: his noble spirit. One day, a serious diphtheria epidemic spreads fast among the children of Nome. When a fierce blizzard closes off all routes of transport, theres no way to obtain lifesaving medicine - unless a team of sled dogs can race 965km through the blinding Arctic storm and bring back anti-toxin. But when the dogs get lost in the frozen wilderness, only Balto can rescue the team and save the children.

Fred Flintstone, a put-upon blue-collar worker struggling to squeak by, with the help of his best buddy Barney and his wife Wilma. After an aptitude test mix up, Fred Flintstone trades his job as Slate and Company Bronto-crane operator for a vice presidency. But theres trouble brewing in Bedrock: An evil executive and his sinister secretary are now plotting to use Fred as the fall guy in an embezzlement scheme!

programme.title: Madagascar: Escape 2 Africa
programme.desc: Alex, Morty and other zoo animals find a way to escape from Madagascar when the penguins reassemble a wrecked airplane. The precariously repaired craft stays airborne just long enough to make it to the African continent. There the New Yorkers encounter members of their own species for the first time. Africa proves to be a wild place, but Alex and company wonder if it is better than their Central Park home.

programme.title: Fred Claus
programme.desc: This is a story youve never heard before, a hilarious and heart warming comedy about Fred Claus, Santas brother - and complete opposite. After growing up in saintly Nicks shadow, Fred becomes a grouch whos lost his belief in Christmas. Then, one magical December, Fred flies north (first class via reindeer) to find brother Nick is in trouble: a scheming efficiency expert is out to shut down Christmas forever! Expect fun by the sleighful as Fred helps save Christmas and rediscovers the gift of family.

programme.title: Balto
programme.desc: Part husky, part wolf, Balto doesnt know where he belongs. Hes an outcast in Alaska, except to his true friends - Boris, the Russian snow goose, polar bear cubs Muk and Luk, and the beautiful husky, Jenna. Even though hes different, all of Baltos friends recognise what he still cant see himself: his noble spirit. One day, a serious diphtheria epidemic spreads fast among the children of Nome. When a fierce blizzard closes off all routes of transport, theres no way to obtain lifesaving medicine - unless a team of sled dogs can race 965km through the blinding Arctic storm and bring back anti-toxin. But when the dogs get lost in the frozen wilderness, only Balto can rescue the team and save the children.

programme.title: Shark Tale
programme.desc: Oscar is a fast-talking little fish whose big dreams have a habit of landing him in hot water. Lenny is a great white shark with a sensitive side and a secret: hes a vegetarian.

programme.title: The Wild Robot
programme.desc: Shipwrecked on a deserted island, a robot named Roz must learn to adapt to its new surroundings. Building relationships with the native animals, Roz soon develops a parental bond with an orphaned gosling.

programme.title: Rise of the Guardians
programme.desc: When an evil spirit known as Pitch lays down the gauntlet to take over the world, the immortal Guardians must join forces for the first time to protect the hopes, beliefs, and imagination of children all over the world.

programme.title: Icons Unearthed: Marvel
programme.desc: By the conclusion of Marvels Phase Two, the Studio had overcome almost every kind of setback and challenge that could be imagined in the filmmaking business. Ant-Man opened number one at the North American box office - the twelfth consecutive Marvel feature to achieve that feat, clearing the way for Marvel to pursue a more varied and ambitious slate of projects, sometimes based on more obscure source material, including Captain Marvel, Black Panther, Doctor Strange, and The Eternals. Feige must have marveled (yup, did that on purpose) at what his kingdom had become. What he had already achieved in film was unprecedented. But he was still chasing a tiny gold statue.

programme.title: Rise of the Billionaires
programme.desc: As the iPhone is launched and we enter the wild world of social media, we watch open-mouthed as the young billionaires wealth goes stratospheric and with it, their desire for power. They are courted by young Senator Obama, who hangs out at Google HQ and pretends to know his coding terms. This awakens the billionaires to their own power, so that they start lobbying - and buying mansions - in Washington DC. But its not all plain sailing: Elon Musks Tesla endeavour nearly bankrupts him during the financial crisis and golden boy Mark Zuckerberg is left sweating on stage when the dark side of tech emerges.

programme.title: Call Me Ted
programme.desc: Ted sells his billboard business, ends his sailing career, and starts the Goodwill Games. He focuses on CNN and his environmental and peace initiatives.

programme.title: Jack L. Warner: The Last Mogul
programme.desc: The epic documentary portrait of the pioneering film producer whose studio, Warner Bros., gave us such Hollywood classics as Little Caesar, The Adventures of Robin Hood, Casablanca, The Maltese Falcon, Yankee Doodle Dandy, Rebel Without A Cause, My Fair Lady, Bonnie and Clyde and hundreds more. Hailed by reviewers as "one of the best films about a movie studio", Jack L. Warner: The Last Mogul reveals the behind-the-scenes story of the man whom Bette Davis, Errol Flynn, James Cagney, Edward G. Robinson, Humphrey Bogart, and Bugs Bunny called "boss". Produced by Jack Warners grandson, Emmy Award-nominated filmmaker Gregory Orr, the film provides an insiders access to memories and material never before seen by the public. Included are rare photographs, home movies, Warner Bros. film clips and exclusive interviews that capture the life and times of a Hollywood legend.

programme.title: Great British Railway Journeys
programme.desc: Michael discovers a hardy breed of sheep on the atmospheric Romney Marsh, explores Kents new sparkling wine industry, and finds out why the Victorians went mad for ferns in Hastings.

programme.title: Icons Unearthed: Marvel
programme.desc: Marvels Phase Two followed the home run that was The Avengers. Guardians Of The Galaxy (2014) would be the fourth instalment of the second phase of Marvels MCU, following Iron Man 3 (2013), Thor: The Dark World (2013) and Captain America: The Winter Soldier (2014). Marvel was cranking them out in rapid succession, but Guardians would represent a radical departure from everything that had come before, exploring two genres that Marvel had yet to attempt - sci-fi space opera, and straight up comedy.

programme.title: Great British Railway Journeys
programme.desc: Michael visits the hometown of Robbie Burns and finds out how to make haggis, discovers how the railways transformed golf in Prestwick, and uncovers the story of the great Victorian tartan hoax in Paisley.

programme.title: Great British Railway Journeys
programme.desc: Michael explores the historic Dumbarton shipyards that built the Cutty Sark, visits one of Queen Victorias favourite haunts, Loch Lomond, and goes hunting for gold in Scotlands mountains.

programme.title: Icons Unearthed: Marvel
programme.desc: By the conclusion of Marvels Phase Two, the Studio had overcome almost every kind of setback and challenge that could be imagined in the filmmaking business. Ant-Man opened number one at the North American box office - the twelfth consecutive Marvel feature to achieve that feat, clearing the way for Marvel to pursue a more varied and ambitious slate of projects, sometimes based on more obscure source material, including Captain Marvel, Black Panther, Doctor Strange, and The Eternals. Feige must have marveled (yup, did that on purpose) at what his kingdom had become. What he had already achieved in film was unprecedented. But he was still chasing a tiny gold statue.

programme.title: Rise of the Billionaires
programme.desc: As the iPhone is launched and we enter the wild world of social media, we watch open-mouthed as the young billionaires wealth goes stratospheric and with it, their desire for power. They are courted by young Senator Obama, who hangs out at Google HQ and pretends to know his coding terms. This awakens the billionaires to their own power, so that they start lobbying - and buying mansions - in Washington DC. But its not all plain sailing: Elon Musks Tesla endeavour nearly bankrupts him during the financial crisis and golden boy Mark Zuckerberg is left sweating on stage when the dark side of tech emerges.

programme.title: Call Me Ted
programme.desc: Ted sells his billboard business, ends his sailing career, and starts the Goodwill Games. He focuses on CNN and his environmental and peace initiatives.

programme.title: Jack L. Warner: The Last Mogul
programme.desc: The epic documentary portrait of the pioneering film producer whose studio, Warner Bros., gave us such Hollywood classics as Little Caesar, The Adventures of Robin Hood, Casablanca, The Maltese Falcon, Yankee Doodle Dandy, Rebel Without A Cause, My Fair Lady, Bonnie and Clyde and hundreds more. Hailed by reviewers as "one of the best films about a movie studio", Jack L. Warner: The Last Mogul reveals the behind-the-scenes story of the man whom Bette Davis, Errol Flynn, James Cagney, Edward G. Robinson, Humphrey Bogart, and Bugs Bunny called "boss". Produced by Jack Warners grandson, Emmy Award-nominated filmmaker Gregory Orr, the film provides an insiders access to memories and material never before seen by the public. Included are rare photographs, home movies, Warner Bros. film clips and exclusive interviews that capture the life and times of a Hollywood legend.

programme.title: Idiot TV
programme.desc: A series of clips featuring the biggest fools on the planet. Its gold medal buffoonery collected and curated like never before, with rewinds, slow-mos and close ups.

programme.title: Ridiculousness
programme.desc: Rob and Steelo welcome Lolo Wood to chug some water in Stayin Hydrated, experience small-town terror in Living in Horrorville and discover the importance of having good aim.

programme.title: Ridiculousness
programme.desc: Rob, Steelo and special guest Lolo Wood break out the instruction manuals for Using Things Wrong, and shine a light on some Shadow Fun.

programme.title: Taskmaster
programme.desc: Evil Greg Davies sets comedians cruel conundrums. Nish Kumar is presented with a coconut harness, while a blindfolded Sally Phillips handles a slice of bread.

programme.title: Two and a Half Men
programme.desc: Charlie decides to have a colonoscopy in order to avoid going on a visit with Chelsea to see her parents. However, when he returns home, he finds a surprise at his house.

programme.title: Two and a Half Men
programme.desc: Alan finds himself locked up after a bar fight, as Charlie worries that Chelsea might be attracted to the lawyer who handles the case.

programme.title: Outback Truckers
programme.desc: Tackling the toughest roads and heaviest loads, Outback Truckers is back for an exciting 6th season! Facing extremes of drought ravaged land to rain drenched roads that leave you stranded for days, these determined truckers battle the elements on every job they do.

programme.title: Outback Car Hunters
programme.sub-title: Ford Falcon XM and Fiat X1/9
programme.desc: The boys make an incredible desert discovery - an ultra-rare Ford Falcon XM delivery sedan; and Italy is the inspiration for a sporty Fiat X1/9 restoration.

programme.title: The Liquidator
programme.desc: Flea market haggler. Storage locker trader. Pawnshop owner. When it comes to moving discarded merchandise Jeff Schwarz has done it all. Jeff has bought and sold his way up the food chain to become the owner of Direct Liquidation, a 30,000-square-foot warehouse chock full of ever-changing oddities, household goods, and urban artefacts that are going to make him rich. Armed with two cell phones, a wallet full of cash and his razor-sharp negotiating skills, Jeff is on the job seven days a week trying to buy low and sell high and most importantly, keep the goods moving. This program will give you a ringside seat to Jeffs fast-paced, high-stakes, buy-and-sell world. From getting the tip and checking out the goods to making the deal and finding a buyer, youll see it all - and it isnt always pretty.

programme.desc: George Jung is the son of Fred, a struggling small business owner. Seeing his family struggle to make ends meet and failing, George vows never to share a similar fate. He then becomes extremely rich by working with Pablo Escabar by importing cocaine into America, but trouble escalates when the FBI are in pursuit.

programme.title: Little Nicky
programme.desc: When Satan reneges on his plans to retire, two of his three heirs leave Hell for New York City to gather enough souls to vote the Prince of Darkness out of office. But Satan sends his youngest and nicest son, Little Nicky, to bring his two treacherous brothers home.

programme.title: Reindeer Games
programme.desc: Just released from prison, all Rudy Duncan wants is to start a new life with Ashley, the girl of his dreams, whom he met through pen pal letters in prison. But between them and happiness stands her crazy brother, Gabriel, and his motley crew of deadly criminals who think Rudy has some inside information about a casino where he once had a job, a casino Gabriel and his short-fused posse plan to take down. Now, just as Rudy is beginning his new life, hes caught in a high-velocity avalanche of temptations and surprises that could bury him, unless he can artfully dodge them.

programme.title: Black Hawk Down
programme.desc: A harrowing war drama where two Black Hawk helicopters are shot down over Mogadishu, trapping an elite team of American soldiers in a 15-hour firefight as they try to recover their fallen comrades.

programme.title: The Fast and the Furious
programme.desc: On the turbo-charged streets of Los Angeles, every night is a championship race. With nitro-boosted fury, Dominic Toretto rules the road, turning all his challengers into dust. He and his rival, Johnny Tran, are the boldest, the baddest, and the best, but now theres new rage on the road. They know hes tough, they know hes fast, but what they dont know is that hes a speed demon detective with enough drive and determination to come out the winner.

programme.title: Jurassic Park III
programme.desc: Desperate to find their missing son, Paul and his wife Amanda trick eminent palaeontologist Dr Alan Grant into accompanying them to Isla Sorna. The small team embark on a dangerous task, searching through a deserted island inhabited by ferocious dinosaurs.

programme.title: Galaxy Quest
programme.desc: For four years, the courageous crew of the NSEA Protector set off on thrilling and often dangerous missions in space - and then their series was cancelled. Now, 20 years later, aliens under attack mistake the Galaxy Quest television transmissions for historical documents and beam up the crew of has-been actors to save the universe. With no script, no director and no clue, the actors must turn in the performances of their lives.

programme.title: Scary Movie
programme.desc: In this send-up of todays most popular horror movies, a familiar-looking group of teenagers find themselves being stalked by a more-than-vaguely recognisable masked killer. As the victims begin to pile up and the laughs pile on, none of your favourite scary movies escape the razor-sharp satire of this outrageously funny parody.

programme.title: Charlies Angels
programme.desc: When a devious mastermind embroils them in a plot to destroy individual privacy, the Angels, aided by their loyal sidekick Bosley, set out to bring down the bad guys. But when a terrible secret is revealed, it makes the Angels targets for assassination.

programme.title: Big Daddy
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, Sonny Koufax is a carefree slob trying to save his love life by becoming responsible. He gets the chance when a cute kid turns up needing a father.

programme.title: Cast Away
programme.desc: A FedEx systems engineers ruled-by-the-clock existence abruptly ends when a harrowing plane crash leaves him isolated on a remote island. As Chuck struggles to survive, he finds that his own personal journey has only just begun.

programme.title: How the Grinch Stole Christmas
programme.desc: Hes mean and green and he hates the yo-ho-hoing. The Grinch conspires to steal Christmas from Whoville, making off with the presents, decorations, trees and every other joyful thing.

programme.title: Meet the Parents
programme.desc: Male nurse Greg Focker is poised to propose to his girlfriend Pam during a weekend stay at her parents home. But heres the catch he needs to ask her father first. Alas, the fur flies as Jack Byrnes, Pams cat-crazy, ex-CIA father takes an immediate dislike to her less-than-truthful beau. Gregs quest for approval gets seriously side-tracked as Murphys Law takes over and a hilarious string of mishaps turns him into a master of disaster and total pariah in the eyes of the entire family, all except for his shell-shocked girlfriend, who cant believe she still lovers her one-man wrecking crew.

programme.title: American Pie
programme.desc: Youll never look at warm apple pie the same way again. This film takes a hysterical look at the goal of four unlucky in love high school friends who make the ultimate pact: lose their virginity by prom night. As they try to manipulate their way into the hearts of some of their classmates, their plans often backfire with hilarity. Follow the raging hormones of four teenage boys and their girls as they gear up for the most important night of their lives: the prom.

programme.title: Almost Famous
programme.desc: A high-school boy in the early 1970s is given the chance to write a story for Rolling Stone magazine about an up-and-coming rock band as he accompanies them on their concert tour.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible II
programme.desc: Special Agent Ethan Hunt teams up with the villains ex-girlfriend to destroy an international conspiracy to sell a deadly virus to the highest bidder.

programme.title: Snatch
programme.desc: Mickey ONeil, a bare knuckles gypsy fighter, is roped in to save the necks of two small-time operators whose scheming collides with that of a lunatic kingpin villain, Brick Top, and a missing diamond smuggler.

programme.title: The Perfect Storm
programme.desc: Its Halloween, 1991. Near Gloucester, Massachusetts, the six members of the Andrea Gail, a swordfishing boat, head out to sea for their last trip of the season. Unbeknownst to them, a shockingly brutal storm is slowly gaining steam. Before the National Weather Bureau has a chance to inform the crew of the impending danger, its too late. The resulting battle with three merging weather fronts, an unheralded natural disaster, is gruelling and tragic. Based on the true-life bestselling novel by Sebastian Junger.

programme.title: The Bone Collector
programme.desc: A murderer is loose on the streets of Manhattan. A diabolical killer whose brutal slayings leave a trail of cryptic messages hidden at the scene of the crime. Clues which only a brilliant mind can interpret. Lincoln Rhyme is a gifted but disabled detective who is assigned to the case as the city becomes gripped with fear. Amelia Donaghy is a feisty, street-smart policewoman, who together with Lincoln, must go inside the mind of this terrifying madman and defeat him at his own game.

programme.title: Bridget Joness Diary
programme.desc: Bridget Jones is a busy journalist and singleton lost amid a sea of smug-marrieds in London. After vowing to abandon her many vices, Bridget turns over a new page by channelling her opinions and insecurities in a journal that becomes a hilarious chronicle of her misadventures. Soon, Bridget finds herself stuck in the sights of not one, but two men: her dashing boss Daniel, who thrives on bad behaviour; and the brooding Mark, who she despises but somehow cant get away from.

Soon, Bridget finds herself stuck in the sights of not one, but two men: her dashing boss Daniel, who thrives on bad behaviour; and the brooding Mark, who she despises but somehow cant get away from.

programme.title: Reindeer Games
programme.desc: Just released from prison, all Rudy Duncan wants is to start a new life with Ashley, the girl of his dreams, whom he met through pen pal letters in prison. But between them and happiness stands her crazy brother, Gabriel, and his motley crew of deadly criminals who think Rudy has some inside information about a casino where he once had a job, a casino Gabriel and his short-fused posse plan to take down. Now, just as Rudy is beginning his new life, hes caught in a high-velocity avalanche of temptations and surprises that could bury him, unless he can artfully dodge them.

programme.title: Little Nicky
programme.desc: When Satan reneges on his plans to retire, two of his three heirs leave Hell for New York City to gather enough souls to vote the Prince of Darkness out of office. But Satan sends his youngest and nicest son, Little Nicky, to bring his two treacherous brothers home.

programme.title: Galaxy Quest
programme.desc: For four years, the courageous crew of the NSEA Protector set off on thrilling and often dangerous missions in space - and then their series was cancelled. Now, 20 years later, aliens under attack mistake the Galaxy Quest television transmissions for historical documents and beam up the crew of has-been actors to save the universe. With no script, no director and no clue, the actors must turn in the performances of their lives.

programme.title: Hairspray
programme.desc: Whos who behind the do? Its 1962 - the 50s are out and change is in the air. Tracey Turnblad, a big girl with big hair and an even bigger heart, has only one passion - dancing. Her dream is realised when she wins a spot on a local TV dance program, which is transformed overnight from outsider to teen celebrity. But can a trendsetter in dance and fashion defeat the programs reigning princess, win the heartthrob Link Larkin, and integrate television without messing up her hairdo?

programme.title: The Prince of Egypt: Live from the West End
programme.desc: A live stage recording of the musical based on DreamWorks Animations 1998 film adapted from the story of Moses, from his being a prince of Egypt to his ultimate destiny of leading the Children of Israel out of Egypt.

programme.title: Trolls
programme.desc: When Troll Village is invaded by the Bergens, two mismatched trolls must try and tolerate each other as they set out on a journey to rescue their friends.

programme.title: Trolls Band Together
programme.desc: Join Poppy and Branch on their latest adventure as they embark on an epic journey that lead to Branchs reunion with his BroZone brothers, and Poppys long-lost sister, Viva.

programme.title: Grease
programme.desc: Things are really hoppin at Rydell High when Danny discovers the object of his summer fling, Sandy, has moved to town and enrolled in his school.

programme.title: The Blues Brothers
programme.desc: After the release of Jake Blues from prison, he and brother Elwood go to visit the orphanage where they were raised by nuns. They learn that the church stopped its support and will sell the place unless the tax on the property is paid within 11 days. The brothers decide to raise the money by putting their blues band back together and staging a big gig. They may be on a mission from God but theyre making enemies everywhere they go.

programme.title: The Watchers
programme.desc: A 28-year-old artist gets stranded in an expansive, untouched forest in western Ireland. Finding shelter, she meets three strangers who are stalked by mysterious creatures every night.

programme.title: Johnny English Strikes Again
programme.desc: The new adventure begins when a cyber-attack reveals the identity of all active undercover agents in Britain, leaving Johnny English as the secret services last hope. Called out of retirement, English dives head first into action with the mission to find the mastermind hacker. As a man with few skills and analogue methods, Johnny English must overcome the challenges of modern technology to make this mission a success.

programme.title: Hot Fuzz
programme.desc: Nicholas Angel is a big-city cop who cant be stopped - but hes making everyone else on the force look bad. When he is reassigned to a small, quiet town, he struggles with this new, seemingly idyllic world and his bumbling partner. But their dull existence is interrupted by several grisly and suspicious accidents, and the crime-fighting duo turn up the heat and hand out high-octane, car-chasing, gun-fighting, big-city justice.

programme.title: Downton Abbey
programme.desc: The continuing story of the Crawley family.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol
programme.desc: Blamed for the terrorist bombing of the Kremlin, IMF operative Ethan Hunt (Tom Cruise) is disavowed along with the rest of the agency when the President initiates Ghost Protocol. Left without any resources or backup, Ethan must find a way to clear his agencys name and prevent another attack. To complicate matters further, Ethan is forced to embark on this mission with a team of fellow IMF fugitives whose personal motives he does not fully know.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
programme.desc: With the IMF disbanded, and Ethan out in the cold, the team now faces off against a network of highly skilled special agents, the Syndicate. These highly-trained operatives are hell-bent on creating a new world order through an escalating series of terrorist attacks. Ethan gathers his team and joins forces with disavowed British agent Ilsa Faust, who may or may not be a member of this rogue nation, as the group faces their most impossible mission yet.

programme.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
programme.desc: On a dangerous assignment to recover stolen plutonium, Ethan Hunt chooses to save his team over completing the mission, allowing nuclear weapons to fall into the hands of a deadly network of highly-skilled operatives intent on destroying civilization. Now, with the world at risk, Ethan and his IMF team are forced to become reluctant partners with a hard-hitting CIA agent as they race against time to stop the nuclear fallout. Theres never been a threat more destructive, stunts so jaw-dropping in the film critics are calling the best "Mission" yet!

programme.title: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
programme.desc: In the brand new adventure Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle, the tables are turned as four teenagers are sucked into the world of Jumanji. When four high-school kids discover an old video game console with a game theyve never heard of Jumanji they are immediately drawn into the games jungle setting, literally becoming the avatars they chose: gamer Spencer becomes a brawny adventurer; football jock Fridge loses (in his words) the top two feet of his body and becomes an Einstein; popular girl Bethany becomes a middle-aged male professor; and wallflower Martha becomes a badass warrior. What they discover is that you dont just play Jumanji you must survive it. To beat the game and return to the real world, theyll have to go on the most dangerous adventure of their lives, discover what Alan Parrish left 20 years ago, and change the way they think about themselves or theyll be stuck in the game forever.

programme.title: Man of Steel
programme.desc: A young boy learns that he has extraordinary powers and is not of this Earth. As a young man, he journeys to discover where he came from and what he was sent here to do. But the hero in him must emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind.

programme.title: Spider-Man: No Way Home
programme.desc: With Spider-Mans identity now revealed, Peter asks Doctor Strange for help. When a spell goes wrong, dangerous foes from other worlds start to appear, forcing Peter to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.

programme.title: Snatch
programme.desc: Mickey ONeil, a bare knuckles gypsy fighter, is roped in to save the necks of two small-time operators whose scheming collides with that of a lunatic kingpin villain, Brick Top, and a missing diamond smuggler.

programme.title: Hitch
programme.desc: Hitch is a cocky and successful date doctor for the unlucky in love, but when he falls for gossip columnist Sara, he forgets his own rules.

programme.title: Split
programme.desc: Kevin has evidenced 23 personalities to his trusted psychiatrist, Dr Fletcher, but there remains one still submerged who is set to materialise and dominate all the others. Compelled to abduct three teenage girls, led by the wilful, observant Casey, Kevin reaches a war for survival among all of those contained within him, as well as everyone around him, as the walls between his compartments shatter apart.

programme.title: Minority Report
programme.desc: In the year 2054, the head of a police unit specialising in pre-crime - the arrest and conviction of murderers before they commit their crime - finds himself accused of a future murder.

programme.title: Talladega Nights: The Ballad of Ricky Bobby
programme.desc: NASCAR stock car racing sensation Ricky Bobby is a national hero because of his "win at all costs" approach. He and his loyal racing partner, childhood friend Cal Naughton Jr., are a fearless duo - "Shake" and "Bake" by their fans for their ability to finish so many races in the #1 and #2 positions, with Cal always in second place. When flamboyant French Formula One driver Jean Girard challenges "Shake" and "Bake" for the supremacy of NASCAR, Ricky Bobby must face his own demons and fight Girard for the right to be known as racings top driver.

programme.title: Tenet
programme.desc: Armed with only one word, Tenet, and fighting for the survival of the entire world, The Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold into something beyond real time. Not time travel. Inversion.

programme.title: The Accountant
programme.desc: Christian Wolff is a math savant with more affinity for numbers than people. Behind the cover of a small-town CPA office, he works as a freelance accountant for some of the worlds most dangerous criminal organisations. With the Treasury Departments Crime Enforcement Division, run by Ray King, starting to close in, Christian takes on a legitimate client: a state-of-the-art robotics company where an accounting clerk has discovered a discrepancy involving millions of dollars. But as Christian uncooks the books and gets closer to the truth, it is the body count that starts to rise.

programme.title: Scream
programme.desc: After a series of mysterious deaths befalls their small town, an offbeat group of friends led by Sidney Prescott become the target of a masked killer. As the body count begins to risine, Sidney her friends find themselves contemplating the "Rules" of horror films as they find themselves living in a real-life one.

programme.title: MaXXXine
programme.desc: Adult film star and aspiring actress Maxine Minx finally gets her big break. However, as a mysterious killer stalks the starlets of LA, a trail of blood threatens to reveal her sinister past.

programme.title: Fast and Furious 7
programme.desc: Targeted by a cold-blooded black ops assassin with a score to settle, their only hope is to get behind the wheel again and secure an ingenious prototype tracking device. Facing their greatest threat yet in places as far away as Abu Dhabi and as familiar as the Los Angeles streets they call home, the crew must come together once again as a team, and as a family, to protect their own.

programme.title: The Bourne Supremacy
programme.desc: Suffering from amnesia, Bourne has left his violent past behind and is living a normal life with girlfriend Marie. But his plans for a peaceful life are crushed when he narrowly escapes an assassination attempt. Now hunted by an unknown enemy, Bourne proves to be neither an easy target nor a person whose skill, determination and resilience can be underestimated.

programme.title: Waterworld
programme.desc: Earth is covered with water and the human race struggles to survive on dilapidated boats and makeshift floating cities. A drifter becomes caught up in the struggle between the evil Deacon and a childs secret key to a wondrous place called "Dryland."

programme.title: Instant Family
programme.desc: Pete and Ellie must learn the ropes of instant parenthood when they bring in three foster children. Inspired by a true story, discover this must-see family comedy from the creators of Daddys Home.

programme.title: Ghostbusters
programme.desc: Armed with proton packs and a new range of kick-ass weapons, the Ghostbusters battle to save the city from an uprising of mischievous ghouls.

programme.title: Despicable Me 2
programme.desc: Gru, his adorable girls, and the mischievous Minions are back with a cast of unforgettable new characters in the blockbuster sequel to the worldwide phenomenon. Just as Gru has given up being super-bad to be a super-dad, the Anti-Villain League recruits him to track down a new criminal mastermind and save the world. Partnered with secret agent Lucy Wilde, Gru, along with the wildly unpredictable Minions, must figure out how to keep his cover while also keeping up with his duties as a father. Get ready for more Minion madness.

programme.title: The Grinch
programme.desc: For their eighth fully animated feature, Illumination and Universal Pictures present "The Grinch," based on Dr. Seuss beloved holiday classic. The Grinch tells the story of a cynical grump who goes on a mission to steal Christmas, only to have his heart changed by a young girls generous holiday spirit. Funny, heartwarming and visually stunning, its a universal story about the spirit of Christmas and the indomitable power of optimism.

Be inspired and encouraged this week, with Joyce Meyer on Enjoying Everyday Life.

programme.title: Overcomer
programme.desc: Life changes overnight for Coach John Harrison when his high school basketball team and state championship dreams are crushed under the weight of unexpected news. When the largest manufacturing plant shuts down and hundreds of families leave their town, John questions how he and his family will face an uncertain future. After reluctantly agreeing to coach cross-country, John and his wife, Amy, meet an aspiring athlete whos pushing her limits on a journey toward discovery. Inspired by the words and prayers of a new-found friend, John becomes the least likely coach helping the least likely runner attempt the impossible in the biggest race of the year.

programme.title: Kids Beach Club
programme.desc: Join the Beach Club Kids as they navigate life, explore character lessons, and have a blast playing memorable games while discovering God through the pages of His Word, the Bible.

programme.title: Torchlighters: Heroes of the Faith
programme.desc: John Bunyan spends his days in prison, separated from his wife and children. Living in the cold, stone cell is the price he pays for going against the established state religion. If only he would agree to stop preaching, John could walk out a free man! Why does he choose to stay in jail, and how will he serve his Lord in this wretched place? Find out in this episode of The Torchlighters.

programme.title: Ancestors: New Testament
programme.desc: Discover how similar we are to our faith ancestors from the New Testament. These hilarious animations reveal more about Bible heroes, villains, and everyday folks that God selected to do extraordinary things.

programme.title: The Catholic Guy
programme.desc: Bruce Downes is The Catholic Guy. Bruce and his team will move, inspire and challenge you to live your life to the absolute fullest. No matter your age, situation or background, be prepared to laugh, learn and listen to what God is trying to say to you. Bruce travels Australia speaking regularly about his experiences in life and in the Church in a way that is both relatable and easy to understand. Bruces message of power, impact, freedom and purpose is for anyone and everyone - for no matter where you are around the world today, God is never far from you.

programme.title: The Incredible Journey
programme.desc: Gary Kent is the speaker for The Incredible Journey. He is an archaeologist who has excavated numerous sites throughout Israel and Jordan. He holds a BA in Theology, MA in Ancient History and Archaeology, and M in Divinity. As an internationally-acclaimed speaker and TV presenter, he has spoken and produced numerous documentaries on subjects including the Bible, Bible prophecy, world events, historical places and natural health. His passion is to share the good news of Jesus soon return.

programme.title: Helping Hands
programme.desc: Helping Hands TV celebrates the people making the world a better place. This inspiring and uplifting program introduces impact-makers and game-chnagers across Australia and facilitates conversations to empower viewers to make a positive impact in their own circles of influence. Discover social enterprise, community groups, business, charities, and individuals driven by passion and purpose to make a positive impact. Each episode features a panel discussion with industry experts and leaders in their field discussing social topics to enable and facilitate impact and change. Panellists include representatives from RUOK?, Paul Ramsay Foundation, Salvation Army, Social Enterprise Australia, Wayside Chapel, Chaplaincy Australia, Australian Defence Force, and many others.

programme.title: Hachi: A Dogs Tale
programme.desc: This film is based on one of the most treasured and heartwarming true stories ever told. Professor Parker Wilson is a distinguished scholar who discovers a lost Akita puppy on his way home from work. Despite initial objections from Wilsons wife, Cate, Hachi endears himself into the Wilson family and grows to be Parkers loyal companion. As their bond grows deeper, a beautiful relationship unfolds embodying the true spirit of family and loyalty, while inspiring the hearts of an entire town.

"This series will look at the wisdom that God has built into the created order, so that we can observe it and put it into practice in our day to day lives." Join us for this inspiring series.

World renowned actors, singers, athletes and ministers share the platform with Dr. Graham. Also often features the famous sounds of the Billy Graham Choir, George Beverly Shea and Cliff Barrows for an hour of blessing and inspiration to all who watch.

programme.title: The Restoration Road
programme.desc: As we travel this side of life, none of us arrives anywhere by accident. We choose, think, pray, and feel our way down a road of desires and intentional acts that bring us to our destination. We program our internal GPS to guide us to one of two places: destruction or restoration. Which direction are you heading? For seventeen years, host, Mitch Kruse was owner, CEO, and auctioneer for Kruse International, the worlds largest collector car sales organisation. Today, Mitch writes and speaks to a wide array of audiences and on The Restoration Road offers sound biblical teaching exploring wisdom, leadership and restoration. Youll be challenged to embrace boldness and holiness, and youll be encouraged to stand firm in your faith, letting your life declare, without question, that you have been with Jesus. Listen now and rediscover your role as a courageous pillar of truth because of your encounter with Jesus!

Computer-controlled blinds, clear to opaque glass, a two-storey helical glass staircase and a custom-designed, air-powered laundry chute are all on the table. As well as a house that can think for itself, Damien wants to fuse green building materials with commercial elements to create a zero-carbon house, not an easy task when youre wanting all the latest wizardry and comforts. Its hard to wrap it all up in a strictly green philosophy.

programme.title: Grand Designs Australia
programme.desc: With his own machinery and the assistance of family and neighbours, industrial designer Mike plans to build a large spotted gum-clad home on French Island (a low-key National Park island near Philip Island which has more koalas than people) with huge exposed spotted gum trusses he will build in his shed and beautifully finished internal walls of dry stacked stone reminiscent of a lofty American ranch-style cabin. He will be transporting materials to the site via his 10-ton truck from the mainland onto a commuter barge. Adding to the challenge is the fact hes doing it all off-grid. This will be a hand-hewn house built from love of a most unusual location.

programme.title: Property Brothers: Forever Home
programme.desc: When Jasmin and Nick found a beautiful century home on a huge property, it immediately reminded Jasmin of the Midwest home she grew up in, and they knew this was to be their forever home.

programme.title: Buying and Selling
programme.desc: Determined to give their twins the best possible education, Beth and Chris want to move to a better district. Drew and Jonathan step in with a plan to transform their aesthetically challenged home.

programme.title: Buying and Selling
programme.desc: Chandra and Tom bought their foreclosure home seven years ago and its been an ongoing DIY disaster ever since. With the entire family desperate to move, Drew and Jonathan step in with a rescue plan.

programme.title: My Dream Home
programme.desc: After more than 30 years in their rented farm home, Carolyn and Gerald are hunting for a rural retirement home of their own. They need plenty of space to entertain family and friends, and its critical they stay in the community they love. Jonathan and Drew step in to make the process pain-free, but finding a sprawling country property that dovetails with their wish list proves tricky. That is, until the search leads them back to Carolyns three-acre family homestead where an ambitious reno has the power to transform the past.

programme.title: Home Town
programme.desc: After years of travelling, a bachelor is ready to purchase a home where his family has resided for five generations, so Ben and Erin find a cottage with resale potential.

programme.title: Fixer to Fabulous

programme.desc: A ballroom-dancing California couple is ready for a renovation and for the Marrs, its their unique home yet. Dave and Jenny take on the project as they aim to create a bathroom spa retreat.

programme.title: My Lottery Dream Home
programme.desc: A NYC couple look to buy a home in Long Island after winning $3 million on a scratchie. In the end, they must decide if they want to purchase a waterfront property or get more value for their money.

programme.title: My Dream Home
programme.desc: James and David are desperate to escape their nightmare townhouse. They want more space, light, and high ceilings. The brothers come to the rescue, helping them find a budget-friendly dream home.

programme.title: Love It or List It Vancouver
programme.desc: A cramped home with a stunning vista has Jillian wondering if she can transform the inside to match the view outside and convince Tony to stay, or will Todd surprise Nicole with a new home?

programme.title: A Place in the Sun
programme.desc: Dartmoor couple Maria and Andy love Cyprus. They met on the island 20 years ago, got married on the island and are now planning the big move to live their permanently.

programme.title: A Place in the Sun
programme.desc: Diane and Gary are searching for a holiday home in the all year round sunshine of Paphos in Cyprus. The property must be wheelchair friendly plus have a pool (as thats non negotiable within the family).

programme.title: A Place in the Sun
programme.desc: Jean Johansson is house hunting with Karen and Richard around Famagusta in eastern Cyprus, showing them five properties for their 200,000-pound budget.

programme.title: Britney Ever After
programme.desc: This is the tumultuous true story of Britney Jean Spears, one of the bestselling teenage music artists of all-time, whose dating life and public emotional breakdowns were the subjects of a worldwide media frenzy. By the age of 21, Britney Spears already had a number one platinum, debut album, a cover on Rolling Stone, a record-breaking second album, and international superstardom. Success in her personal life, however, would be much harder to achieve. A well-publicized romance and break-up with Justin Timberlake, a three-day marriage to a childhood sweetheart, and an ill-fated marriage to back-up dancer Kevin Federline made for a chaotic contrast to her record-setting music career.

programme.title: Menendez: Blood Brothers
programme.desc: Erik and Lyle Menendez were educated, nice boys from sunny Beverly Hills, California. Erik was an exceptional tennis player and Lyle was studying at Princeton University. So when their parents were found shot dead in their home, no one could figure out why they would have done it? Everyone was perplexed. Was it for Money? For Fame? The case seemed closed, but that;s when the brothers revealed that they were sexually molested throughout their childhoods by their father, Jose. This was the trial that no one was ready for. Our story follows Erik and Lyle as they struggle with their overwhelming guilt, the harsh reality of abuse, incest and molestation that lead them down this path and the trial that shocked an entire nation of television watchers. Never before seen details emerge as we look closer into the lives of the Menendez brothers.

programme.title: The Bear Lake Murders
programme.desc: A sheriff teams up with a detective to uncover the truth behind a series of annual deaths in a resort town. Their investigation leads them to believe that a killer is preying on holidaymakers.

programme.title: Oscar Pistorius: Blade Runner Killer
programme.desc: The true story of the sprint runner dubbed theBlade Runner; and his rise to fame as a gold medalist Paralympic champion and as the first double-leg amputee to participate in the Olympics. Oscars resilience to overcome his disability combined with his apparent fairy tale relationship with model Reeva Steenkap turned him into a media favorite. This all shattered one Valentines Day night when four bullets were fired and Reevas life was taken. Her brutal death shocked the world and the court room drama that followed consumed the news.

programme.title: Nightmare in the Desert
programme.desc: A woman returns home hoping to move on, but finds herself fighting for survival in the desert when someone tries to prevent her boyfriends surprise proposal, even through murder.

programme.title: Murder in Nashville
programme.desc: A woman gets swept up in a whirlwind romance with the son of a wealthy power player in the country music scene.

programme.title: Crowdsource Murder
programme.desc: A friend encourages Monica to start a crowdsource fund to pay for her daughters hospital bills. However, when a seemingly generous man donates more and more money, she begins to question his motives.

programme.title: Stalked by My Amish Boyfriend
programme.desc: Carly develops a relationship with Abram, a young Amish man. Their seemingly innocent courtship soon takes a dark turn when Abram refuses to return home.

programme.title: Amish Stud: The Eli Weaver Story
programme.desc: A man who calls himself Amish Stud plots with his mistress to murder his wife, to the horror of his conservative Amish community.

programme.title: Michael Jackson: Searching for Neverland
programme.desc: Based on Bill and Javons book Remember the Time: The Last Days of Michael Jackson, this movie will chronicle those intimate moments between Jackson and his children, document the professional turbulence that engulfed Jackson in financial trouble and forced him back to rehearsals for the ill-fated This Is It tour that led to his early death, and help answer the question that fans around the world want to know: What really happened to the King of Pop?

programme.title: V.C Andrews Ruby
programme.desc: In the heart of the bayou, Ruby Landry lives a simple, happy life. The only family Ruby Landry has ever known are her loving guardian, Grandmere Catherine, a Cajun spiritual healer, and her drunken, outcast Grandpere Jack. Her life is filled with hope and promise, especially when her attraction for handsome Paul Tate blossoms into a mysterious, wonderful love. But Pauls wealthy parents forbid him to associate with a poor Landry while Grandmere urges her to follow her dream of becoming a great painter. In a faded photograph, Ruby glimpses for the first time the image of her father and learns of a shameful deception and a shocking scheme of blackmail that now must come to light. Stunned by these revelations, she is devastated when Grandmere dies, leaving her to seek out her father in his vast New Orleans mansion. There, in a house of lies, madness, and cruel torment, Ruby clings to her memories of Paul to keep her heart alive. For only their love can save her now.

programme.title: Britney Ever After
programme.desc: This is the tumultuous true story of Britney Jean Spears, one of the bestselling teenage music artists of all-time, whose dating life and public emotional breakdowns were the subjects of a worldwide media frenzy. programme.title: Girl in the Basement
programme.desc: Inspired by true events, this is the story of Sarah, a teenager imprisoned by her father in the basement of their family home for over twenty years. The father told his wife and other children that Sarah had run away to be with a boyfriend the family disapproved of. Meanwhile, as the years went by, he would secretly visit her in the basement, raping her there while her mother and siblings continued living upstairs. Sarah gave birth alone in the basement to several children. Her father let her raise one there but brought the others upstairs, claiming to his wife that Sarah has left the grandchildren on their doorstep. When Sarah finally escapes, the family learns the devastating truth about what had been going on for years right beneath their feet.

programme.title: Who Killed JonBenet?
programme.desc: This Lifetime Original Movie revisits the infamous murder of pint-sized beauty queen JonBenet Ramsey and the lurid details that captivated the nation. Starting with the 911 call and investigation lead by Detective Steve Thomas, the film provides a closer look into what exactly happened the day after Christmas 1996, when she was found beaten and strangled in the familys basement. With the addition of recently surfaced information, the film takes a fresh look at the events and the competing theories about the murder. Were Patsy and John Ramsey responsible or covering for someone else in the family? Was this a kidnapping gone wrong, or was this the work of a predator who had seen JonBen t in one of her pageants? Twenty years after the tragic events, the question remains: Who killed JonBenet?

programme.title: The Pastors Wife
programme.desc: Mary, a dutiful preachers wife and mother of three, becomes the prime suspect in her husbands murder. What went on behind this perfect familys closed doors? Based on a true story.

programme.title: Secrets of Eden
programme.desc: A small-town minister is accused of the deaths of two beloved parishioners when evidence surfaces that the family wasnt quite as perfect as they appeared.

programme.title: Cyberstalker
programme.desc: Thirteen years ago, Aidens world was torn apart after an online stalker followed her into the real world and broke into her home to claim the object of his desire. The resulting night of terror ended with the murders of both Aidens mother and father. The stalker escaped the scene without Aiden seeing his face; he is gone without a trace, an unknown man, a murderer now watching Aidens every move. To escape this danger Aiden spends the next 13 years offline, in therapy and secluded anonymity. Who should Aiden trust in a web of deception where no one may be who they seem? There is nowhere for Aiden to hide when someone wants to love her to death. Mischa Barton, Dan Levy and Ron Lea star. (2012)

programme.title: The Perfect Teacher
programme.desc: When spoiled, beautiful high-schooler Devon sets her sights on her handsome teacher, she wont take no for an answer.

programme.title: Blonde and Blonder
programme.desc: When two dim-witted blonde bombshells are mistaken for the underworlds most cunning assassins, they are approached with a lucrative contract to take out the head of the Chinese mafia in a globetrotting, air-headed comedy. Two fair-haired beauties have just witnessed a high-profile mob hit, and now the Godfather is convinced that they have what it takes to rub out his most fearsome rival. After accepting a hearty payout and agreeing to carry out the dangerous assignment, the two brainless beauties hit the open road on the adventure of a lifetime.

programme.desc: Two mothers battle to see which of their overachieving daughters will be accepted to a prestigious university. However, when one of their methods quickly spirals out of control, the games turn deadly.

June agrees to help him pay off the extortionist, but when the woman is found dead, June becomes the prime suspect.

programme.title: Who Is Killing The Cheerleaders?
programme.desc: Ellie, a former cheerleader, returns to her high school as a teacher ten years after she was nearly killed in a series of brutal slayings on the squad. When the attacks start up again shortly after her arrival, she must find the killer before they get to her first.

programme.title: Man with my Husbands Face
programme.desc: When a womans husband disappears during a kayak trip, everyone assumes that he drowned. When she catches a glimpse of a man who looks exactly like him, it sets off a chain of events.

programme.title: Its Beginning to Look a Lot Like Murder
programme.desc: In the middle of preparing for her business biggest season, Diana Hart learns she inherited an old house from her beloved aunt who was murdered.

programme.title: The Night Stalker
programme.desc: Known to many as the "Night Stalker", Richard Ramirez was a cruel and prolific serial killer who murdered 14 people and terrorized Los Angeles in the summer of 1985. This film tells the story of Kit (Bellamy Young), an attorney who travels to San Quentin on an impossible mission to clear the name of Harrison Johnson (Hawthorne James), a death row inmate in Texas whom she believes has been wrongly accused of murders perpetrated by Ramirez (Lou Diamond Phillips). Kit lived in Los Angeles during the fear-tinged summer where Ramirez terrified its citizens and confronting him dredges up old and frightening memories of her own past. As the days count down to the Texas mans execution, Kit confronts Ramirez about his unspeakable crimes in search of an elusive confession, plunging into intense psychological depths in her quest for the truth.

programme.title: Ill Be Watching
programme.desc: Based on the novel The Purple Rose by Christi R. Walsh. After narrowly escaping the clutches of a deadly stalker, a beautiful young woman flees to a remote anonymous town, where she rebuilds her life and finds the man of her dreams, until the man of her nightmares tracks her down.

programme.title: Girl in the Box
programme.desc: In 1977, 22-year-old Colleen Stan doesnt think twice when she hitch hikes and is picked up by a young couple, Cameron and Janice Hooker. But the life she knows is completely ripped away when the couple abducts her and takes her to their home where Cameron tortures and sexually abuses her. For the next seven years, Colleen is imprisoned for up to 23 hours a day, in a coffin-sized box hidden beneath the couples bed. When not incarcerated, Colleen is part of a strange new life as a live-in slave, babysitter, and victim of Camerons bizarre and extreme sexual fantasies.

programme.title: Kidnapping in the Grand Canyon
programme.desc: When two best friends hiking the Grand Canyon trust an experienced hiking guide to bring them on an off trail adventure, things go south when he takes them captive, and they have to fight both man and nature to make it out.

programme.title: Secrets In The Desert
programme.desc: While on a road trip through the desert, Charlie and her boyfriend Aidan break down in the middle of nowhere. While Aidan waits for a tow truck, Charlie heads to a nearby diner to find help. When Aidan goes missing, Charlie finds herself stranded in a strange town unsure who to trust. The only thing she knows is she might just be their only chance to get out alive.

This film tells the story of Kit (Bellamy Young), an attorney who travels to San Quentin on an impossible mission to clear the name of Harrison Johnson (Hawthorne James), a death row inmate in Texas whom she believes has been wrongly accused of murders perpetrated by Ramirez (Lou Diamond Phillips). Kit lived in Los Angeles during the fear-tinged summer where Ramirez terrified its citizens and confronting him dredges up old and frightening memories of her own past. As the days count down to the Texas mans execution, Kit confronts Ramirez about his unspeakable crimes in search of an elusive confession, plunging into intense psychological depths in her quest for the truth.

programme.title: Ill Be Watching
programme.desc: Based on the novel The Purple Rose by Christi R. Walsh. After narrowly escaping the clutches of a deadly stalker, a beautiful young woman flees to a remote anonymous town, where she rebuilds her life and finds the man of her dreams, until the man of her nightmares tracks her down.

programme.title: Girl in the Box
programme.desc: In 1977, 22-year-old Colleen Stan doesnt think twice when she hitch hikes and is picked up by a young couple, Cameron and Janice Hooker. But the life she knows is completely ripped away when the couple abducts her and takes her to their home where Cameron tortures and sexually abuses her. For the next seven years, Colleen is imprisoned for up to 23 hours a day, in a coffin-sized box hidden beneath the couples bed. When not incarcerated, Colleen is part of a strange new life as a live-in slave, babysitter, and victim of Camerons bizarre and extreme sexual fantasies.

programme.title: Kidnapping in the Grand Canyon
programme.desc: When two best friends hiking the Grand Canyon trust an experienced hiking guide to bring them on an off trail adventure, things go south when he takes them captive, and they have to fight both man and nature to make it out.

programme.title: Secrets In The Desert
programme.desc: While on a road trip through the desert, Charlie and her boyfriend Aidan break down in the middle of nowhere. While Aidan waits for a tow truck, Charlie heads to a nearby diner to find help. When Aidan goes missing, Charlie finds herself stranded in a strange town unsure who to trust. The only thing she knows is she might just be their only chance to get out alive.

programme.desc: In Modesto, California, a young mother is brutally murdered in her home. Police find Debi Whitlocks nearly decapitated body lying in the hallway. There is blood on the walls. Her nightgown is pulled over her face and a knife lays between her legs. Even worse, her three-year-old daughter is sleeping just feet away. Except for her purse, nothing in the house is missing or out of place. Could she have known her killer? As the investigation unfolds, police zero in on two suspects - her husband who she had recently reconciled with, and her boyfriend. The question is, can a mothers love help to track down a killer?

programme.title: Crimes That Shook Britain
programme.desc: Dr Harold Shipman is one of the Worlds biggest serial killers. In 2000 he was convicted of murdering 215 patients by lethal injection. For over 20 years this general practitioner worked under the guise of a kind, caring man of the community. Whilst fooling his family, colleagues and patients he preyed on those who trusted them the most and killed them with an injection of diamorphine. Such a trusted pillar of the community, Shipman, went unquestioned for years killing men and women in the small town of Hyde, in the UK. His cover was eventually blown when he tried to forge one victims will. The true devastation unravelled revealing the doctor to be one of the worlds biggest single serial killers of all time. Shipman never revealed his motive and committed suicide in prison in 2004. This film documents Shipmans horrendous crimes told by the people who were affected by his crimes. Danny Mellors mother was murdered by the GP. Danny and other relatives were shocked. She d been in good health just days before. Lesley Creaseys Auntie was killed by Shipman after a routine visit to her house. She appeared fit and well to neighbours just hours before. Dr Raj Patel worked across the road from Shipman countersigning death certificates for years. His detective work along with his colleagues helped bring the murderer to justice. Debbie Massey is an undertaker who worked with Shipman. Her suspicions helped to raise the alarm.

With their resources stretched to the limit, police uncover few clues but plenty of rumours. Why would anyone want to kill the Blairsville dentist? Was the motive money or a bitter divorce? And when a state trooper becomes the prime suspect, can police be trusted to investigate one of their own?

programme.title: Cold Blood
programme.desc: In Modesto, California, a young mother is brutally murdered in her home. Police find Debi Whitlocks nearly decapitated body lying in the hallway. There is blood on the walls. Her nightgown is pulled over her face and a knife lays between her legs. Even worse, her three-year-old daughter is sleeping just feet away. Except for her purse, nothing in the house is missing or out of place. Could she have known her killer? As the investigation unfolds, police zero in on two suspects - her husband who she had recently reconciled with, and her boyfriend. But with little evidence, the case goes cold for everyone - except Debi Whitlocks mother. She refuses to give up and for six years she keeps her daughters case alive in the media. The question is, can a mothers love help to track down a killer?

programme.title: Crimes That Shook Britain
programme.desc: Dr Harold Shipman is one of the Worlds biggest serial killers. In 2000 he was convicted of murdering 215 patients by lethal injection. For over 20 years this general practitioner worked under the guise of a kind, caring man of the community. Whilst fooling his family, colleagues and patients he preyed on those who trusted them the most and killed them with an injection of diamorphine. Such a trusted pillar of the community, Shipman, went unquestioned for years killing men and women in the small town of Hyde, in the UK. His cover was eventually blown when he tried to forge one victims will. The true devastation unravelled revealing the doctor to be one of the worlds biggest single serial killers of all time. Shipman never revealed his motive and committed suicide in prison in 2004. This film documents Shipmans horrendous crimes told by the people who were affected by his crimes. Danny Mellors mother was murdered by the GP. Danny and other relatives were shocked. She d been in good health just days before. Lesley Creaseys Auntie was killed by Shipman after a routine visit to her house. She appeared fit and well to neighbours just hours before. Dr Raj Patel worked across the road from Shipman countersigning death certificates for years. His detective work along with his colleagues helped bring the murderer to justice. Debbie Massey is an undertaker who worked with Shipman. Her suspicions helped to raise the alarm.

A remarkable administrator and ruler, Genghis Khans system of khanites- the means by which he ruled conquered lands - lasted for more than 400 years after his death.

programme.title: Dogfights

State-of-the-art computer graphics are used to recreate famous battles. programme.title: History of Warfare
programme.desc: Alongside its sister series Blood and Steel, this is the definitive guide to the military history of the world from the Roman Empire to the bloody battles in Normandy during World War II. Both series provide the viewer with military history as it should be: exciting, vivid and action-packed. It leads the way in authoritative and entertaining historical programming, providing vivid accounts of the conflicts which have helped to shape our modern world. This is the story of a new form of warfare to which Germanys enemies had no answer - the lightning war - Hitlers terrifying, ruthless but highly effective tactic which brought countries such as Poland and Czechoslovakia to their knees during the early months of World War II. Originally conceived during the Great War, the Germans added air power and the crucial element of political surprise to the concept of Blitzkrieg.

programme.title: Burlesque
