Ali has a chance to make her dreams come true, if only she could make the right choices.

programme.title: The High Note
programme.desc: This musical comedy-drama is set amidst the glitz and glamour of the Los Angeles music scene. Grace Davis is a middle-aged singing icon who hasnt released a new record in a decade. Maggie is Graces overworked personal assistant who has long dreamed of becoming a music producer. While Graces manager would rather her play it safe and perform the same show night after night, Maggie and Grace believe the time has come to sing a new tune.

programme.title: Single White Female
programme.desc: Hedy Carlson and Allie Jones - two women taken to their most primal extremes from which only one can emerge. When Allie throws out her two-timing boyfriend, Hedy suddenly appears to help her fight off the urges to call him back. The surviving half of a set of twins, Hedy seeks someone to complete her, and sees in the chic and articulate Allie everything she would like to be so she not only moves into the apartment, but into the most personal aspects of Allies life, even going so far as to have her hair styled the same. But when Allie reconciles with her boyfriend, their unspoken bargain goes terrifyingly awry. Instincts dont come baser than this.

programme.title: Ladies in Black
programme.desc: Adapted from the bestselling novel by Madeleine St John, Ladies In Black is an alluring and tender-hearted comedy drama about the lives of a group of department store employees in 1959 Sydney.

programme.title: Girls Trip
programme.desc: When four lifelong friends travel to New Orleans for the annual Essence Festival, sisterhoods are rekindled, wild sides are rediscovered, and theres enough dancing, drinking, brawling and romancing to make the Big Easy blush.

programme.title: Crazy Rich Asians
programme.desc: Crazy Rich Asians follows native New Yorker Rachel Chu (Constance Wu) as she accompanies her longtime boyfriend, Nick Young (Henry Golding), to his best friends wedding in Singapore. Excited about visiting Asia for the first time but nervous about meeting Nicks family, Rachel is unprepared to learn that Nick has neglected to mention a few key details about his life. It turns out that he is not only the scion of one of the countrys wealthiest families but also one of its most sought-after bachelors. Being on Nicks arm puts a target on Rachels back, with jealous socialites and, worse, Nicks own disapproving mother (Michelle Yeoh) taking aim. And it soon becomes clear that while money cant buy love, it can definitely complicate things.

A recently-fired national news anchor who is afraid she will lose her son the way she has just lost her career, Viola does everything she can to scare off her sons new fiance by becoming the worlds worst mother-in-law. While Violas long-time assistant Ruby does her best to help Viola execute her crazy schemes, Charlie decides to fight back and the gloves come off as the women battle it out to see just who the alpha-female is.

programme.title: Honey: Rise Up And Dance
programme.desc: Aspiring street dancer Skyler is at a major crossroads in her life. Shes decided to try out for the same dance crew as her formally trained sister Tosha in order to compete for a college scholarship, but is discouraged by her family and boyfriend who doubt that her raw, edgy talent is enough for her to win. Determined to prove them all wrong, Skyler practices non-stop in Atlantas underground dance scene and catches the eye of Tyrell. He helps her take her sexy dance and hip-hop battle skills to the next level in order to achieve her dreams.

programme.title: Life Without Dick
programme.desc: In this dark romantic comedy Colleen Gibson, heir to the Rose Red Grapefruit fortune, whose cheating boyfriend Dick is coincidently taken out before singing hitman Daniel has a chance to do the job himself. When Daniel and Colleen meet, sparks fly and Daniel soon discovers that his potential new girlfriend is a much better killer than he is.

programme.title: This Is Where I Leave You
programme.desc: When their father dies, four grown siblings, bruised and banged up by their respective adult lives, are forced to return to their childhood home and live under the same roof together for a week.

programme.title: The First Wives Club
programme.desc: Join Diane Keaton, Bette Midler and Goldie Hawn in this sinfully satisfying revenge romp about a trio of first wives who team up to teach their lying, cheating ex-husbands a lesson. Ivana Trumps galvanising cameo - dont get mad, dahlinks, get everytink - sets the scene in a comedy that hinges on the self-mockery of its ageless stars. Midlers ball-busting shtick, Keatons ditsy vulnerability and Hawns eternal youth are just light-hearted grist for the mill of female friendship as a serious source of strength.

programme.desc: Four lifelong friends have their lives forever changed after reading 50 Shades of Grey in their monthly book club.

programme.desc: An overbearing, blind, and retired lieutenant colonel hires a young guardian to assist him. They embark on a wild weekend trip that will change the lives of both men forever.

programme.title: Here and Now
programme.desc: Vivienne, is an established singer with a successful music career, but after receiving some devastating news ahead of her upcoming world tour, she is forced to reassess her life, the decisions shes made and the relationships shes sacrificed to get there. Still reeling from the shock, she finds herself navigating the busy streets of New York City but feeling more alone than ever before. In the 24 hours that follow she must find a way to make peace with her life choices and the people she left behind including her overbearing mother, Jeanne, her long-time manager, Ben, her ex-husband, Nick and her old friend Tessa before she embarks on the next chapter of her life.

programme.title: Honey: Rise Up And Dance
programme.desc: Aspiring street dancer Skyler is at a major crossroads in her life. Shes decided to try out for the same dance crew as her formally trained sister Tosha in order to compete for a college scholarship, but is discouraged by her family and boyfriend who doubt that her raw, edgy talent is enough for her to win. Determined to prove them all wrong, Skyler practices non-stop in Atlantas underground dance scene and catches the eye of Tyrell. He helps her take her sexy dance and hip-hop battle skills to the next level in order to achieve her dreams.

programme.title: Life Without Dick
programme.desc: In this dark romantic comedy Colleen Gibson, heir to the Rose Red Grapefruit fortune, whose cheating boyfriend Dick is coincidently taken out before singing hitman Daniel has a chance to do the job himself. When Daniel and Colleen meet, sparks fly and Daniel soon discovers that his potential new girlfriend is a much better killer than he is.

programme.title: This Is Where I Leave You
programme.desc: When their father dies, four grown siblings, bruised and banged up by their respective adult lives, are forced to return to their childhood home and live under the same roof together for a week.

programme.title: The First Wives Club
programme.desc: Join Diane Keaton, Bette Midler and Goldie Hawn in this sinfully satisfying revenge romp about a trio of first wives who team up to teach their lying, cheating ex-husbands a lesson. Ivana Trumps galvanising cameo - dont get mad, dahlinks, get everytink - sets the scene in a comedy that hinges on the self-mockery of its ageless stars. Midlers ball-busting shtick, Keatons ditsy vulnerability and Hawns eternal youth are just light-hearted grist for the mill of female friendship as a serious source of strength.

programme.title: Friends with Benefits
programme.desc: Justin Timberlake and Mila Kunis star as best friends who are both coming out of disastrous relationships. They decide to make a friends with benefits pact vowing to stop the casual sex if either become emotionally attached. While the set-up works at first, soon the two friends fall in love and must re-evaluate what they mean to each other.
